    • Method Detail

      • set

        public static void set​(VirtualMachine vm)
        Sets currently displayed virtual machine. If new virtual machine to display is different than the one displayed now, all registered listeners are called.
        Parameters:
        vm - virtual machine to display or null, if no machine should be displayed now.
        See Also:
        addListener(VmEmptyListener), addListener(VmChangeListener), addListener(VmUpdateListener)

      • unset

        public static void unset()
        Sets current virtual machine to null. If some virtual machine was displayed before calling this method, it will call all registered listeners.
        See Also:
        set(VirtualMachine)
